    "description": "&quot;Galactic Gladiators&quot; is a 2D top-down shooter game. You control a spaceship and face off against hordes of enemies as you progress through levels. At each level, you can choose a card that will grant unique abilities to help you defeat your opponents. Additionally, you can collect crystals to upgrade your ship or buy a new and more powerful one. The ultimate goal is to get as far as possible, defeating bosses and facing increasingly challenging obstacles. Test your combat skills in space with &quot;Galactic Gladiators&quot;.<br><br>At the start, the player only begins with the basic attributes of the starting ship.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309470/extras/06cc944074dc6c71091a883933e75944.avif?t=1677283539\" width=220 height=456 /></span><br><br>At the end of each round, the player can choose a new skill card to use passively in the next level.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309470/extras/b1b7b8305913f8c753bde66967c88f6f.avif?t=1677283539\" width=580 height=420 /></span><br><br>The game features:<br>- 3 ships.<br>- 19 card options.",
